snippet: Powell, a Jamaican, was the evening’s star attraction in the absence of his countryman Usain Bolt, the world-record holder, who pulled out with a blocked joint in his left leg.
abstract: Asafa Powell wins 100 meters at Diamond League track meet in Paris; other event winners noted.
lead_paragraph: Powell, a Jamaican, was the evening’s star attraction in the absence of his countryman Usain Bolt, the world-record holder, who pulled out with a blocked joint in his left leg.
